                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I see no way that a single spell can fix things for enchanters as a class.  The minimum number I can see (off the cuff from work, at least) is 2:
<br />

<br />
Improved Slow
<br />

<br />
WoM Upgrade
<br />

<br />
They can replace the DoT upgrade (what were they thinking with that one?) with one of those, and perhaps Mayhem with the other.  They then need to finish making Wake of Felicity into a proper Fascination upgrade.
<br />

<br />
Basically, they need to rethink the enchanter spells from the start, including both the order they are obtained via rune turn-in and the specifics of the others (i.e.:  how about WIS/INT cap increase on C6 in keeping with the Shaman buffs?  Allowing SoSalik to buff haste OVER the cap, but not as high as bards can?  Making Color Snap last 8 seconds, even if we only get 6 from it--at least it wouldn't LOOK like a nerf that way?  Adding 100hp to our self-HP/AC buff, which is needed across the board for ALL INT casters, IMO, including a bit more AC, too?  I came up with these in less time than it took me to type them at work--why can't the people who get paid to think of this stuff do at least as well?).  
<br />

<br />
A damn Eldritch Rune upgrade to get it stacking with Ethereal Rune is needed, too...if 450 points didn't break the game in upgrading Arcane Rune, then 450 on Eldritch won't either.  I won't even begin to go into the micro-managing that had to have gone into some of the number tweaking in ALL spell lines...come on, 33 HP reduction in Steeloak prior to going live?  ...would 2k on AR/ER have been too big a leap?  
<br />

<br />
One of the repeating themes in most of our issues is that the paternalistic tone in SoE's attitude is grating on our adult sensabilities, and this is the problem which I have the hardest time understanding.
<br />

<br />
Anyway...just hoping that the patch addresses at least a few of our concerns...we'll see next week...</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=570078" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Teyvan M'Crae</a>
