And yes, I am out there also looking for a replacement. Since SOE saw fit to reduce me to doing things I didn't start out doing, and which were not my classes abilities when I started, and since aside from one class defining spell line (Mana Regen) all others got mutilated into what they are today... they can go take a long walk off a short pier.
<br />
The very second I find something that will hold my interest... Sony have lost a customer who had at one point 8 accounts running, and is now down to 3 which will all be cancelled when I find a replacement...</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
